OL,3,CSon says 'it's time to let mum lay in
OL,4,Cpeace' 16 years on from her death
OL,6,FThe son of a woman from Dumfries says
OL,7,F"it's time to let mum finally lay in
OL,8,Fpeace" 16 years on from her death in
OL,9,FGreece after a defendant has been
OL,10,Fquestioned in connection to her death
OL,11,Fby police.
OL,13,FJean Hanlon, 53, moved to the Greek
OL,14,Fisland to start a new life but went
OL,15,Fmissing and was found dead in the sea
OL,16,Foff the harbour of the capital
OL,17,FHeraklion on 13 March 2009.
