OL,3,CSon says 'it's time to let mum lay in
OL,4,Cpeace' 16 years on from her death
OL,6,FHer death was previously ruled as
OL,7,Fdrowning but in 2023, the Greek
OL,8,Fauthorities confirmed her death was a
OL,9,Fresult of foul play.
OL,11,FHer son Michael Porter always believed
OL,12,Fshe was murdered and has campaigned
OL,13,Ftirelessly to find out what happened.
OL,15,FHe said: "Now we're coming to the end,
OL,16,Fit's time to let mum finally lay in
OL,17,Fpeace and let mum get the justice she
OL,18,Fdeserves.
