OL,3,CSon says 'it's time to let mum lay in
OL,4,Cpeace' 16 years on from her death
OL,6,F"Nothing will ever change the fact
OL,7,Fthat our mum is gone. I do think how
OL,8,Fshe died and how she was disrespected
OL,9,Fhas robbed us of the proper grieving
OL,10,Fprocess."
OL,12,FJean's family have campaigned for
OL,13,Fyears to pressure the Greek
OL,14,Fauthorities into opening a new
OL,15,Finvestigation.
OL,17,FThey also hired their own private
OL,18,Finvestigator. Mr Porter added: "This
OL,19,Fcampaign is nearly reaching two
OL,20,Fdecades now, what a whirlwind - I
OL,21,Fwouldn't wish it on anybody.
