OL,3,CSon says 'it's time to let mum lay in
OL,4,Cpeace' 16 years on from her death
OL,6,F"It's been one massive learning curve
OL,7,Fas a person, I grew up with this case
OL,8,Finto an adult. I chose that, the
OL,9,Ffamily chose that - we would choose it
OL,10,Fagain but it hasn't come without its
OL,11,Fissues.
OL,13,F"It's also brought a lot of good. The
OL,14,Fpeople we've met through charities,
OL,15,Fthe people who have sponsored us or
OL,16,Fhelped with the various shows we've
OL,17,Fput on.
